  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/716567d24998064e3d22c8ba49783c3d.webp?t=1717745145\" width=398 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/01f5df83c9513f4d8f2f4d0ca5519c99.avif?t=1717745145\" width=616 height=257 /></span><br>Take your hammer and get the coals burning! It's time for fire, metal and magic! In this game you will: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Forge, bend, cut and sharpen metal. Work with wood and bone.<br></li><li>Weave chainmail. Use potions and spells.<br></li><li>Take blacksmithing orders, creating unique weapons, armor and other curious items.<br></li><li>Upgrade your dwelling and forge.<br></li><li>Find useful items and new friends who are willing to help. <br></li><li>Explore high fantasy world while diving into the story of the game.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/30e4ce6cdd929c54faf643b1dbbe1f72.webp?t=1717745145\" width=297 height=40 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5fbf5eb8b7d9ad1432d33f6c6f441160.poster.avif?t=1717745145\" width=630 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5fbf5eb8b7d9ad1432d33f6c6f441160.webm?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5fbf5eb8b7d9ad1432d33f6c6f441160.mp4?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You'll have to work in the forge literally by hand - grab the hammer and hit the workpiece with it, sending out sparks. Strike after strike to flatten or bend metal. Cut wooden boards, sticks and branches by grasping the saw handle and moving it back and forth. Tie ropes, attach chains. Push the levers of the tongs. Bring flasks to the blanks, spill potions. Use magic books to enchant blades, shields and armor! There are over 100 unique and repeatable schemes, as well as a free-to-play forge mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/44aba67995f51139998ce184f0fcfef3.poster.avif?t=1717745145\" width=630 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/44aba67995f51139998ce184f0fcfef3.webm?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/44aba67995f51139998ce184f0fcfef3.mp4?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/65aa53a5ab946caa96d12fbafd1f03bf.webp?t=1717745145\" width=356 height=40 /></span><br>Much of what you find during your wanderings will prove useful in the forge. The properties of items and character skills are revealed in combinations with each other. It's no secret, for example, that dwarves are more willing to work in the forge if you put a couple of kegs of beer in the house!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5123459d38a9ea3def7e9dd49fa831be.poster.avif?t=1717745145\" width=630 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5123459d38a9ea3def7e9dd49fa831be.webm?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5123459d38a9ea3def7e9dd49fa831be.mp4?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/981923b764e0c7705e318fa940f6da57.webp?t=1717745145\" width=188 height=40 /></span><br>You have a journey ahead of you, blacksmith. You have seen it in your dreams. And now they lead you. So embrace it. Embark on your adventure and face your destiny!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5e112180bc599cb24a756bcf2cf0dfd8.poster.avif?t=1717745145\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5e112180bc599cb24a756bcf2cf0dfd8.webm?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2531370/extras/5e112180bc599cb24a756bcf2cf0dfd8.mp4?t=1717745145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
